headline: Garmin's new all-in-one SERV+ display offers a smart RV experience
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced SERV+™ —the ultimate control panel for travelers who want a smart RV experience with a sleek, modern touchscreen display. Serving as command central for the RV, drivers and passengers can easily control onboard entertainment, monitor security camera feeds, change the temperature settings and adjust other systems throughout the cabin — all from a single screen. And for a hands-free option, voice commands can control systems from anywhere in the RV.
